{"id": "1215685762989826118", "channel_id": "1212267053570850826", "type": 0, "author_id": "232848201500065792", "author_name": "hananichiya", "author_bot": false, "content": "我就想問一件事", "timestamp": "2024-03-08T15:41:12.246000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1212267053570850826", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：「幻夢深潛」的調整計劃", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1215685786872062033", "channel_id": "1212267053570850826", "type": 0, "author_id": "232848201500065792", "author_name": "hananichiya", "author_bot": false, "content": "尤烏那個B我已經不管了", "timestamp": "2024-03-08T15:41:17.940000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1212267053570850826", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：「幻夢深潛」的調整計劃", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1215685825048739850", "channel_id": "1212267053570850826", "type": 0, "author_id": "232848201500065792", "author_name": "hananichiya", "author_bot": false, "content": "菲因特這隻角色到底是拿來幹嘛的", "timestamp": "2024-03-08T15:41:27.042000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1212267053570850826", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：「幻夢深潛」的調整計劃", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1215687645779468388", "channel_id": "1212267053570850826", "type": 0, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "收到大家的反饋了，這個嘗試或許的確失敗，抱歉。沒有預想的難，但對自由度的限制反過來比預想的高。這就違背初衷了。\n\n讓幻夢深潛就是鼓勵速攻，而禁區則慢速更可考慮或許是更合適的。", "timestamp": "2024-03-08T15:48:41.138000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1212267053570850826", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：「幻夢深潛」的調整計劃", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1215687835881832468", "channel_id": "1212267053570850826", "type": 0, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "我們的主要目標首先是剝離融蝕之珠的獎勵與分數無關。這部分會保持。", "timestamp": "2024-03-08T15:49:26.462000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1212267053570850826", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：「幻夢深潛」的調整計劃", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1215687973090234370", "channel_id": "1212267053570850826", "type": 0, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "但分數評價大體會考慮近期還原。但仍然保留癲狂挑戰模式的存在。", "timestamp": "2024-03-08T15:49:59.175000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1212267053570850826", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：「幻夢深潛」的調整計劃", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1215688165575237732", "channel_id": "1212267053570850826", "type": 0, "author_id": "371624648078524416", "author_name": "devis0212", "author_bot": false, "content": "我覺得回合分這樣是可以的 速攻以及其他能有個加分項 譬如：六回合每低於一回合能夠加分", "timestamp": "2024-03-08T15:50:45.067000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1212267053570850826", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：「幻夢深潛」的調整計劃", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1215688253467000872", "channel_id": "1212267053570850826", "type": 0, "author_id": "1188482378948165682", "author_name": "phantom_ye", "author_bot": false, "content": "什么时候让融灾滚出去？一说上难度就是融灾，轮转无光变成了融灾，主线也加融灾，深潜也加融灾，除了融灾不会做别的吗", "timestamp": "2024-03-08T15:51:06.022000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1212267053570850826", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：「幻夢深潛」的調整計劃", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1215688352968351754", "channel_id": "1212267053570850826", "type": 0, "author_id": "1188482378948165682", "author_name": "phantom_ye", "author_bot": false, "content": "换点tag都当有诚意了来来回回就那几个debuff恶心人", "timestamp": "2024-03-08T15:51:29.745000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1212267053570850826", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：「幻夢深潛」的調整計劃", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1215689324889374770", "channel_id": "1212267053570850826", "type": 0, "author_id": "232848201500065792", "author_name": "hananichiya", "author_bot": false, "content": "感覺八回合會是比較合理的速度\n大概是正常流程可以抽乾兩次牌庫的流程", "timestamp": "2024-03-08T15:55:21.469000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1212267053570850826", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：「幻夢深潛」的調整計劃", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1215689439565848627", "channel_id": "1212267053570850826", "type": 0, "author_id": "232848201500065792", "author_name": "hananichiya", "author_bot": false, "content": "六回合的話有時候極端情況第四回合覺醒才上手\n後兩個回合全是打擊防禦沒操作空間", "timestamp": "2024-03-08T15:55:48.810000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1212267053570850826", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：「幻夢深潛」的調整計劃", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1215689813550694481", "channel_id": "1212267053570850826", "type": 0, "author_id": "232848201500065792", "author_name": "hananichiya", "author_bot": false, "content": "道中營運骰出爛造物爛症狀還可以通過商店買刻印或造物彌補\n王關的運氣成分就不要那麼重了", "timestamp": "2024-03-08T15:57:17.975000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-03-08T15:58:35.809000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1212267053570850826", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：「幻夢深潛」的調整計劃", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1215690216418054155", "channel_id": "1212267053570850826", "type": 0, "author_id": "232848201500065792", "author_name": "hananichiya", "author_bot": false, "content": "純運氣不如就改成進場跟王剪刀石頭布就好", "timestamp": "2024-03-08T15:58:54.026000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1212267053570850826", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：「幻夢深潛」的調整計劃", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1215690348735758367", "channel_id": "1212267053570850826", "type": 0, "author_id": "1129819110683988019", "author_name": "anyang0v0", "author_bot": false, "content": "融災會讓純混沌變得很🤡每次開大開銀鑰都加上限，這怎麼玩", "timestamp": "2024-03-08T15:59:25.573000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🤡", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1212267053570850826", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：「幻夢深潛」的調整計劃", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1215690794292351047", "channel_id": "1212267053570850826", "type": 0, "author_id": "232848201500065792", "author_name": "hananichiya", "author_bot": false, "content": "另外再次吐槽\n鼓勵玩家使用黑印，作為與進場就有加成的爆擊和傷害強效相對\n為道中營運，用前期弱勢換後期強勢的屬性定位的話\n應該判定的是玩家實際使用掉的黑印而不是剩下的黑印比較合人性吧", "timestamp": "2024-03-08T16:01:11.802000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-03-08T16:01:22.902000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1212267053570850826", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：「幻夢深潛」的調整計劃", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1215690972441214976", "channel_id": "1212267053570850826", "type": 0, "author_id": "232848201500065792", "author_name": "hananichiya", "author_bot": false, "content": "當然你要說\n喔如果你疊黑印\n人家剩一百塊花不掉的時候你有兩百塊可以花掉一百", "timestamp": "2024-03-08T16:01:54.276000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1212267053570850826", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：「幻夢深潛」的調整計劃", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
